OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChildren 'distraught' after
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FSats reading paper         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Parents and teachers of Year 6 pupils  
OL,6, say a Sats reading paper was so        
OL,7, difficult it left children in tears.   
OL,9,FOne mother told the BBC that her child,
OL,10,Fwho loves reading, was unable to finish
OL,11,Fthe paper.                             
OL,13,FA head teachers' union said even staff 
OL,14,Fhad struggled to understand the        
OL,15,Fquestions, and it would be raising     
OL,16,Fconcerns about the paper.              
OL,18,FThe Department for Education (DfE) said
OL,19,Fit worked to ensure that "all tests are
OL,20,Fappropriate".                          
